entities.game

Class GameStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.game.GameStatus

  • public class GameStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    GameStatus handles the status of an Game. Available information are the version, up-to-date state, download- and extractionprogress.
    Since:
    1.0
